ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/593280/extras/820830d0c04975079ea5a9993a5290bd.avif?t=1756984217\" alt=\"Soundtrack\" width=780 height=100 /></span><br>Experience an enchanting orchestral score inspired by classic RPGs!<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/593280/extras/8652d8d5575757d2b55048c9a5aba6f7.webp?t=1756984217\" width=780 height=30 /></span>",
